headline.main: UN Atomic Chief Expects US Cooperation on Iran Nuke Pact
headline.print_headline: UN Atomic Chief Expects US Cooperation on Iran Nuke Pact

lead_paragraph: The head of the U.N. agency monitoring the Iran nuclear deal says he emphasized the benefits of the pact in a meeting with U.S. Secretary of State Rex Tillerson and says he is confident his message was heard.
